cast.overview: In 1997, before the visit of the pope to Rio de Janeiro, Captain Nascimento from BOPE (Special Police Operations Battalion) is assigned to eliminate the risks of the drug dealers in a dangerous slum nearby where the pope intends to be lodged.
cast.title: Elite Squad

details.biography: Fernanda de Freitas Sahdo (São José do Rio Preto, February 25, 1980) is a Brazilian actress and presenter, winner of the Best Actress award at the Paulínia Film Festival, she also accumulates nominations for a Guarani Award and a Quality Brazil Award.
details.name: Fernanda de Freitas
details.place_of_birth: São José do Rio Preto, São Paulo, Brazil
